channel.title: Rune-Mafia offical
channel.description:
Hello,
Well me and my mate been coding a server
Features so far
Combat (attack, defence, str, hp, prayer) Full fletching (interfaces) Full cooking (interfaces) Full fishing (loops and stops fishing when bag is full) Agility (nearly full not teleporting :) ) Mining Woodcutting Firemaking
I will post pictures when iam less busy coding the server :)
The server client.java is only 150kb at this time beening going to clean it more when its done :o And got over 20 diffent handlers what are for skills and such
The server sould be up in 2 days dedi hosted :)
~T X
